name: F... Rates
description:
This work is part of my project Vertical Horizon. This is a project to change my photography habits and many photographers I see, who usually or always only shoot horizontally objects in front of them according to their point of view. I tried to change the angle of my camera to shoot vertically up or down. well just like that, very simple but the results are really beyond expectations.

JPG / 2500px X 2000px
